LOCUS       pdCas9_(GB1079)         7194 bp    DNA     circular SYN 15-DEC-2025
DEFINITION  Provides the human codon optimized CDS of Cas9 protein with mutated
            (D10A, H840A) and inactivated catalytic domains as a level 0
            GoldenBraid part for C-terminal fusions.
